                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 14040/29.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Wilson</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Buenos Aires</hi>
                        </placeName> (<hi rend="italic">Received</hi>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1909-02-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 25, 1909</hi>
                        </date>).</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Reports that the supreme court has granted the unconditional extradition of
                    Damiano, and that agent and prisoner leave on March 10 on steamship <hi
                        rend="italic">Verdi.</hi>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
